Record Class Movie.Member

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
cs1302.oracle.model.Movie.Member
Enclosing class:
Movie
public static record Movie.Member(String name) extends Record
Represents a "member" record. The objects of this class can describe the cast members, directors, and writers for a movie.
